elements.name: Como usuario accedo a la plataforma Ghost, agregó la información de un nuevo miembro valido y se crea correctamente

steps.name: I am correctly authenticated with "<USERNAME>" and "<PASSWORD>"
I go to the members page
I want to add a new member
I fill in the member name with "<MEMBER_NAME>" and email with "<MEMBER_EMAIL>"
I press the save button to create the new member
The member is successfully created and listed in the members page
